        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I did have a valid reason with the svelte server crashing in projects that were set up with deno, because it did not find a root directory. The changes I made fixed that problem for me and I did not have problems when I tested those changes locally, neither with svelte or the other servers.\n\nMy assumption was wrong that this meant it would work for all projects. So by all means revert it. I'm not using deno anymore for these projects anyway.",
